 Veho will also regularly send drivers a push notification informing them when routes are available.; ; Veho operates 7 days a week in most markets, however some markets may have varying operating days and times.; ; ; ; Do I need to bring my driver's license?; ; It is Veho policy that all drivers maintain a current and valid driver’s license while performing delivery services with Veho.
